BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (If you feel constantly on edge, exhausted, overwhelmed, or emotionally reactive, your) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (nervous system may be dysregulated. This workbook teaches you to recognize your nervous) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (system state, use evidence-based tools to return to safety and calm, and build resilience) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (over time.) Tj ET
endstream
