86 0 obj
<< /Length 2498 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 5: Somatic Tools & Body-Based Practices) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Why Body-Based Tools Work) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (The nervous system speaks the language of the body. You cannot think your way out of a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (dysregulated state - you must work through the body to signal safety to the brain.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 612.4 Td (Shaking and Tremoring) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.4 Td (Animals shake after a threat to discharge survival energy. Humans can too:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.4 Td (- Stand with slightly bent knees) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.4 Td (- Begin gentle bouncing or shaking) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (- Let the shaking spread naturally to whole body) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.4 Td (- Continue for 5-15 minutes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (- Notice what happens as you slow down) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 494.6 Td (Grounding Techniques) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 472.6 Td (Feet on Floor) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.6 Td (- Press feet firmly into the ground) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.6 Td (- Notice the sensation of support beneath you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 428.6 Td (- Rock weight forward, back, side to side) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 414.6 Td (- Stomp gently if needed for more sensation) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 396.6 Td (Butterfly Hug \(bilateral stimulation\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.6 Td (- Cross arms over chest, hands on shoulders) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366.6 Td (- Alternately tap left, right, left, right) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.6 Td (- Slow rhythm for 2-3 minutes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 338.6 Td (- Used in EMDR for emotional processing) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 308.8 Td (Progressive Muscle Relaxation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 290.8 Td (Tense each muscle group for 5 seconds, then release completely:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 276.8 Td (- Start with feet, work up through body to face) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 262.8 Td (- Notice the contrast between tension and release) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 248.8 Td (- Takes 10-15 minutes for full body) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 219.0 Td (Containment Visualization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 201.0 Td (- Imagine a container \(box, vault, locked chest\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 187.0 Td (- Mentally place overwhelming feelings/memories inside) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 173.0 Td (- Close and lock the container) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 159.0 Td (- You can return to it when ready and resourced) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 145.0 Td (- Useful for managing flashbacks or overwhelm) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
